# Optional: enable encrypted sync (Supabase, Sydney ap-southeast-2)
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

# Optional: anonymised product analytics (PostHog). Omit in dev to disable.
# Uses a first-party PostHog cookie so returning visitors are recognised as the same person.
# Production routes events through the Cloudflare Worker at /ingest (see worker/index.ts).
# VITE_POSTHOG_KEY=phc_your_project_token
# VITE_POSTHOG_HOST=/ingest
# VITE_POSTHOG_UI_HOST=https://us.posthog.com

# Support contact form (Cloudflare Worker + Resend). Set the API key as a Worker secret:
# npx wrangler secret put RESEND_API_KEY
# Verify fair-go.ai in Resend, then use a from address on that domain (wrangler.jsonc vars).
